reviewText: Its good but you can find the same stuff on youtube for free
It was okay. Just a combination of old show clips.
Good video.  Discussed the concepts.  What I was looking for.
There is great value in this DVD. I noticed instant results in my shooting capabilities and saving in ammunition.

A good refresher.  My shooting improved immediately.  Your dad and grandpa will for sure have pointers for you but it's good to get some outside help.  The camera angles down the barrel will put the leads into perspective for different species and shot angles.
Great info, beautiful locations, great hunting footage.

So far its the best wing shooting DVD I have seen and learned new technique about
Wing shooting, its very fruitful.
